{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"I'm here today to talk to you\nabout a very powerful little word,"},{"time":5520,"text":"one that people will do almost anything"},{"time":8080,"text":"to avoid becoming."},{"time":10280,"text":"Billion-dollar industries thrive"},{"time":12560,"text":"because of the fear of it,"},{"time":14360,"text":"and those of us who undeniably are it"},{"time":17560,"text":"are left to navigate a relentless storm"},{"time":19920,"text":"surrounding it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22120,"text":"I'm not sure if any of you have noticed,"},{"time":24880,"text":"but I'm fat."},{"time":27600,"text":"Not the lowercase,\nmuttered-behind-my-back kind,"},{"time":30600,"text":"or the seemingly harmless\nchubby or cuddly."},{"time":34000,"text":"I'm not even the more sophisticated\nvoluptuous or curvaceous kind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39720,"text":"Let's not sugarcoat it."},{"time":41720,"text":"I am the capital F-A-T kind of fat."},{"time":45600,"text":"I am the elephant in the room."},{"time":50040,"text":"When I walked out on stage,"},{"time":51600,"text":"some of you may have been thinking,"},{"time":53320,"text":"\"Aww, this is going to be hilarious,"},{"time":55760,"text":"because everybody knows\nthat fat people are funny.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":58400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60440,"text":"Or you may have been thinking,\n\"Where does she get her confidence from?\""},{"time":64599,"text":"Because a confident fat woman\nis almost unthinkable."},{"time":68800,"text":"The fashion-conscious\nmembers of the audience"},{"time":71040,"text":"may have been thinking how fabulous I look"},{"time":73720,"text":"in this Beth Ditto dress --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75320,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76560,"text":"thank you very much."},{"time":78480,"text":"Whereas some of you might have thought,"},{"time":80400,"text":"\"Hmm, black would have been\nso much more slimming.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":83080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":84360,"text":"You may have wondered, consciously or not,"},{"time":86880,"text":"if I have diabetes, or a partner,"},{"time":89840,"text":"or if I eat carbs after 7pm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93360,"text":"You may have worried\nthat you ate carbs after 7pm last night,"},{"time":97320,"text":"and that you really should renew\nyour gym membership."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101320,"text":"These judgments are insidious."},{"time":103600,"text":"They can be directed\nat individuals and groups,"},{"time":106200,"text":"and they can also\nbe directed at ourselves."},{"time":109360,"text":"And this way of thinking\nis known as fatphobia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113800,"text":"Like any form of systematic oppression,"},{"time":116240,"text":"fatphobia is deeply rooted\nin complex structures"},{"time":119920,"text":"like capitalism, patriarchy and racism,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and that can make it\nreally difficult to see,"},{"time":126800,"text":"let alone challenge."},{"time":129000,"text":"We live in a culture"},{"time":130280,"text":"where being fat\nis seen as being a bad person --"},{"time":135280,"text":"lazy, greedy, unhealthy, irresponsible"},{"time":139120,"text":"and morally suspect."},{"time":141440,"text":"And we tend to see thinness"},{"time":143040,"text":"as being universally good --"},{"time":146040,"text":"responsible, successful,"},{"time":148080,"text":"and in control of our appetites,\nbodies and lives."},{"time":152240,"text":"We see these ideas again and again"},{"time":154600,"text":"in the media, in public health policy,"},{"time":157560,"text":"doctors' offices,"},{"time":159200,"text":"in everyday conversations"},{"time":161400,"text":"and in our own attitudes."},{"time":163880,"text":"We may even blame fat people themselves"},{"time":166880,"text":"for the discrimination they face"},{"time":168480,"text":"because, after all, if we don't like it,\nwe should just lose weight."},{"time":173200,"text":"Easy."},{"time":175360,"text":"This antifat bias has become\nso integral, so ingrained"},{"time":179880,"text":"to how we value ourselves and each other"},{"time":182440,"text":"that we rarely question why\nwe have such contempt for people of size"},{"time":188200,"text":"and where that disdain comes from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190960,"text":"But we must question it,"},{"time":192920,"text":"because the enormous value\nwe place on how we look"},{"time":196120,"text":"affects every one of us."},{"time":199000,"text":"And do we really want to live in a society"},{"time":201560,"text":"where people are denied\ntheir basic humanity"},{"time":204520,"text":"if they don't subscribe\nto some arbitrary form of acceptable?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210200,"text":"So when I was six years old,"},{"time":211960,"text":"my sister used to teach ballet\nto a bunch of little girls in our garage."},{"time":216520,"text":"I was about a foot taller and a foot wider\nthan most of the group."},{"time":220400,"text":"When it came to doing\nour first performance,"},{"time":222560,"text":"I was so excited\nabout wearing a pretty pink tutu."},{"time":227200,"text":"I was going to sparkle."},{"time":230800,"text":"As the other girls slipped easily\ninto their Lycra and tulle creations,"},{"time":234960,"text":"not one of the tutus\nwas big enough to fit me."},{"time":238720,"text":"I was determined not to be\nexcluded from the performance,"},{"time":242880,"text":"so I turned to my mother"},{"time":245720,"text":"and loud enough for everyone to hear"},{"time":248680,"text":"said, \"Mom, I don't need a tutu."},{"time":252320,"text":"I need a fourfour.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":254520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":257760,"text":"Thanks, Mom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":262560,"text":"And although I didn't\nrecognize it at the time,"},{"time":265000,"text":"claiming space for myself\nin that glorious fourfour"},{"time":268280,"text":"was the first step towards becoming\na radical fat activist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274080,"text":"Now, I'm not saying\nthat this whole body-love thing"},{"time":276720,"text":"has been an easy skip along\na glittering path of self-acceptance"},{"time":281000,"text":"since that day in class."},{"time":282920,"text":"Far from it."},{"time":284760,"text":"I soon learned that living outside\nwhat the mainstream considers normal"},{"time":288960,"text":"can be a frustrating and isolating place."},{"time":292640,"text":"I've spent the last 20 years unpacking\nand deprogramming these messages,"},{"time":297360,"text":"and it's been quite the roller coaster."},{"time":300880,"text":"I've been openly laughed at,\nabused from passing cars"},{"time":304920,"text":"and been told that I'm delusional."},{"time":307400,"text":"I also receive smiles from strangers"},{"time":309880,"text":"who recognize what it takes\nto walk down the street"},{"time":312720,"text":"with a spring in your step\nand your head held high."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315320,"text":"(Cheer)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":316680,"text":"Thanks."},{"time":318040,"text":"And through it all, that fierce\nlittle six-year-old has stayed with me,"},{"time":322120,"text":"and she has helped me\nstand before you today"},{"time":325000,"text":"as an unapologetic fat person,"},{"time":328040,"text":"a person that simply refuses to subscribe"},{"time":331160,"text":"to the dominant narrative"},{"time":332600,"text":"about how I should move\nthrough the world in this body of mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336320,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344240,"text":"And I'm not alone."},{"time":346440,"text":"I am part of an international\ncommunity of people"},{"time":349600,"text":"who choose to, rather\nthan passively accepting"},{"time":352240,"text":"that our bodies are\nand probably always will be big,"},{"time":356200,"text":"we actively choose to flourish\nin these bodies as they are today."},{"time":361280,"text":"People who honor our strength\nand work with, not against,"},{"time":365080,"text":"our perceived limitations,"},{"time":367480,"text":"people who value health"},{"time":369320,"text":"as something much more holistic"},{"time":371800,"text":"than a number on an outdated BMI chart."},{"time":375000,"text":"Instead, we value mental health,\nself-worth and how we feel in our bodies"},{"time":381120,"text":"as vital aspects\nto our overall well-being."},{"time":385560,"text":"People who refuse to believe\nthat living in these fat bodies"},{"time":388800,"text":"is a barrier to anything, really."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393400,"text":"There are doctors, academics and bloggers"},{"time":396680,"text":"who have written countless volumes"},{"time":398880,"text":"on the many facets\nof this complex subject."},{"time":402720,"text":"There are fatshionistas\nwho reclaim their bodies and their beauty"},{"time":407640,"text":"by wearing fatkinis and crop tops,"},{"time":410600,"text":"exposing the flesh\nthat we're all taught to hide."},{"time":414200,"text":"There are fat athletes"},{"time":415800,"text":"who run marathons,\nteach yoga or do kickboxing,"},{"time":419800,"text":"all done with a middle finger\nfirmly held up to the status quo."},{"time":425560,"text":"And these people have taught me\nthat radical body politics"},{"time":429080,"text":"is the antidote\nto our body-shaming culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433760,"text":"But to be clear, I'm not saying\nthat people shouldn't change their bodies"},{"time":438480,"text":"if that's what they want to do."},{"time":440600,"text":"Reclaiming yourself can be one\nof the most gorgeous acts of self-love"},{"time":444600,"text":"and can look like\na million different things,"},{"time":447920,"text":"from hairstyles to tattoos\nto body contouring"},{"time":451720,"text":"to hormones to surgery\nand yes, even weight loss."},{"time":455320,"text":"It's simple: it's your body,"},{"time":457640,"text":"and you decide what's best to do with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460920,"text":"My way of engaging in activism"},{"time":463840,"text":"is by doing all the things\nthat we fatties aren't supposed to do,"},{"time":466960,"text":"and there's a lot of them,"},{"time":468520,"text":"inviting other people to join me\nand then making art about it."},{"time":473720,"text":"The common thread\nthrough most of this work"},{"time":475800,"text":"has been reclaiming spaces that are\noften prohibitive to bigger bodies,"},{"time":480480,"text":"from the catwalk to club shows,"},{"time":483440,"text":"from public swimming pools\nto prominent dance stages."},{"time":488280,"text":"And reclaiming spaces en masse\nis not only a powerful artistic statement"},{"time":493440,"text":"but a radical community-building approach."},{"time":497120,"text":"This was so true of \"AQUAPORKO!\" --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":499960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":501920,"text":"the fat fem synchronized swim team"},{"time":504560,"text":"I started with a group\nof friends in Sydney."},{"time":508400,"text":"The impact of seeing\na bunch of defiant fat women"},{"time":511800,"text":"in flowery swimming caps and bathers"},{"time":514039,"text":"throwing their legs in the air\nwithout a care"},{"time":516880,"text":"should not be underestimated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":524440,"text":"Throughout my career, I have learned\nthat fat bodies are inherently political,"},{"time":530040,"text":"and unapologetic fat bodies"},{"time":532160,"text":"can blow people's minds."},{"time":536360,"text":"When director Kate Champion,"},{"time":538760,"text":"of acclaimed dance theater\ncompany Force Majeure,"},{"time":541760,"text":"asked me to be the artistic associate"},{"time":544240,"text":"on a work featuring all fat dancers,"},{"time":547560,"text":"I literally jumped at the opportunity."},{"time":551640,"text":"And I mean literally."},{"time":554720,"text":"\"Nothing to Lose\" is a work made\nin collaboration with performers of size"},{"time":558920,"text":"who drew from their lived experiences"},{"time":561520,"text":"to create a work as varied\nand authentic as we all are."},{"time":566080,"text":"And it was as far from ballet\nas you could imagine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570120,"text":"The very idea of a fat dance work\nby such a prestigious company"},{"time":574960,"text":"was, to put it mildly, controversial,"},{"time":579080,"text":"because nothing like it had ever been done\non mainstream dance stages before"},{"time":584120,"text":"anywhere in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587200,"text":"People were skeptical."},{"time":589800,"text":"\"What do you mean, 'fat dancers?'"},{"time":593400,"text":"Like, size 10, size 12 kind of fat?"},{"time":598840,"text":"Where did they do their dance training?"},{"time":601920,"text":"Are they going to have the stamina\nfor a full-length production?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":606760,"text":"But despite the skepticism,"},{"time":608720,"text":"\"Nothing to Lose\" became\na sellout hit of Sydney Festival."},{"time":612840,"text":"We received rave reviews, toured,"},{"time":615200,"text":"won awards and were written about\nin over 27 languages."},{"time":619760,"text":"These incredible images of our cast\nwere seen worldwide."},{"time":625440,"text":"I've lost count of how many times\npeople of all sizes"},{"time":630000,"text":"have told me that the show\nhas changed their lives,"},{"time":633120,"text":"how it helped them\nshift their relationship"},{"time":635160,"text":"to their own and other people's bodies,"},{"time":637520,"text":"and how it made them confront\ntheir own bias."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641440,"text":"But of course, work\nthat pushes people's buttons"},{"time":644800,"text":"is not without its detractors."},{"time":647960,"text":"I have been told\nthat I'm glorifying obesity."},{"time":651320,"text":"I have received violent death threats"},{"time":653840,"text":"and abuse for daring to make work\nthat centers fat people's bodies and lives"},{"time":659320,"text":"and treats us as worthwhile human beings\nwith valuable stories to tell."},{"time":666040,"text":"I've even been called"},{"time":667640,"text":"\"the ISIS of the obesity epidemic\" --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":670600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":672320,"text":"a comment so absurd that it is funny."},{"time":676000,"text":"But it also speaks to the panic,"},{"time":678800,"text":"the literal terror,"},{"time":680800,"text":"that the fear of fat can evoke."},{"time":683600,"text":"It is this fear that's feeding\nthe diet industry,"},{"time":687000,"text":"which is keeping so many of us\nfrom making peace with our own bodies,"},{"time":691800,"text":"for waiting to be the after-photo"},{"time":694120,"text":"before we truly start to live our lives."},{"time":697400,"text":"Because the real elephant\nin the room here is fatphobia."},{"time":702480,"text":"Fat activism refuses to indulge this fear."},{"time":706560,"text":"By advocating for self-determination\nand respect for all of us,"},{"time":710880,"text":"we can shift society's reluctance\nto embrace diversity"},{"time":714840,"text":"and start to celebrate the myriad ways\nthere are to have a body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721760,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}